@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ecgofb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.68 * v0 + 0.94)))
    v2 = (tmp + wp.exp((v1 + 0.96 * v2 + 0.07)))
    v0 = 0.76
    data[tid] = v0
